CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 23, 1950 reads: "The Champ - Bill Winston, left, is shown receiving a trophy symbolic of his winning the pre-holiday handicap tournament at Hillvue last week. Jap Washington, Steel City League prexy, presents the award. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Bill Winston receiving trophy for pre-holiday handicap tournament from Jap Washington, posed in Hillvue Bowling Alley
